    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S) In nomine domini dei eterni, anno ab incarnatione eius millesimo
                        centesimo octuagesimo quinto, sexto nonus madii, indictione tertia.
                        Venditionis contractus (…). <persName ref="#people/3226"
                            >Castracanis</persName> olim filius <persName ref="#people/3214"
                            >Ubertelli</persName> et <persName><name ref="Castraleo"
                                >Castraleone</name></persName> filius eius atque <persName><name
                                ref="Willa">Guillia</name></persName> uxor eiusdem Castracanis
                        necnon et <persName><name ref="Adalasia">Adalascia</name></persName> uxor
                        Castraleonis (…) nos iamdicte femine <foreign>interrogate da</foreign>
                        <persName key="#Judge"><name ref="Ieronimus">Ieronimi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudicis</rs> (…) vendimus et huius rei gratia tradimus
                        atque concedimus tibi <persName><name ref="Petrus"
                        >Petroni</name></persName>, rectori <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/3206"
                            key="#Hospitals"><rs key="#Hospitals">hospitalis</rs>
                            <placeName ref="#places/3207" key="#Hospitals"
                            >Altepascensis</placeName></orgName>, tuisque successoribus in perpetuum
                        videlicet unam terre petiam positam in plagis et finibus <placeName
                            ref="#places/3210" key="#Rivers">Putei</placeName>, in loco qui vocatur
                        Vignale. Cuius confines sunt hii: de una parte est <persName><name
                                ref="Bernardus">Bernardi</name></persName>, de alia <rs
                            key="#Rivers">flumen Iussiana</rs>, a tertia vero <persName
                            ref="#people/3217">Adimari</persName> filii <persName ref="#people/3218"
                            >Alberti</persName>, a quarta autem est predicti hospitalis et
                        aliquantulum dicti Bernardi. Infra totam que est stariora quactuordecim (…).
                        Prezzo: quinquaginta sex lib. bonorum denariorum pisani (…). Pena: in duplum
                        (…). Actum <placeName ref="#places/3227">Gangalandi</placeName>. Signa
                        manuum iamdictorum vinditorum qui hanc cartulam ut supra legitur fieri
                        rogaverunt. Signa manuum Bernardi filii <persName><name ref="Sigismundus"
                                >Sesmundi</name></persName> et <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Pacaloctus">Pacaloci</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Hugo">Ugetti</name></persName> germanorum
                        filiorum <persName><name ref="Hugolinus Hubaldus">Ugolini
                            Ubaldini</name></persName> rogatorum <rs key="#Witness">testium</rs>.
                        (S) Ieronimus iudex predictas mulieres interrogavi atque notavi, huic
                        instrumento completionem imposui. </ab>
                </div>
